  id: case_stolen_prototype
  title: The Stolen Research Prototype
  description: 'A prototype for an advanced navigation system has gone missing from
    the laboratory. Three suspects were present: Dr. Chen (lead researcher), Alex
    (lab technician), and Morgan (security guard). You must investigate the testimonies,
    cross-examine claims, and determine what happened.'
  difficulty: 1
  purpose: 4
  tags: []
  estimatedPlayTimeMinutes: 5
  version: 1
  author: Ivandry
  courtSetup:
