  witnesses:
  - id: 8766827e4c3e4bb7b988844e3474e7f3
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: afb5c64e1c6e34f40bd77f5375bfeaa4, type: 2}
    role: 2
    description: Lead researcher on the Navigation Project. Last person to see the
      prototype before it disappeared.
    testimonies:
    - id: 7898dd4c16a14b438931270d652d27a3
      title: The Lab that Morning
      description: ' Dr. Chen describes the events leading up to the discovery of
        the theft.'
      statements:
      - id: 99e5bbd7972d4178ac31c51c815273f7
        text: I arrived at the lab at 6 AM as usual. The prototype was on my desk
          where I left it yesterday.
        initiallyVisible: 1
        nextStatementId: eb598063d999428e98ae72ef8619062d
        claims:
        - id: b80a717ed8ad40a6a01047b0c5a93a72
          factId: fact_prototype_on_desk
          isTrue: 1
          evaluationRules: []
      - id: 77132c3c61b74aaebdc89104af2bc524
        text: Around 8 AM, I stepped out to grab coffee. I was gone for maybe 10
          minutes.
        initiallyVisible: 1
        nextStatementId: 
        claims:
        - id: 8c6bf91600ae4f8eacd0f574a9f85ec9
          factId: fact_chen_left_lab
          isTrue: 1
          evaluationRules:
          - evaluationType: 0
            requiredEvidence: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 2c0d74d7ca190413a9e98fc4758fd5a7, type: 2}
            successEffects:
            - effect: 8
              targetType: 0
              targetId: 
              courtStat: 0
              operation: 0
              characterStat: 0
              value: 2
            failureEffects:
            - effect: 8
              targetType: 0
              targetId: 
              courtStat: 1
              operation: 0
              characterStat: 0
              value: 1
      - id: c523e8f1394542acbd28f0fad473583d
        text: When I returned, the prototype was gone. I immediately checked with
          Alex and Morgan, but neither had seen it.
        initiallyVisible: 1
        nextStatementId: 
        claims:
        - id: 03c623e1d20748a1bbda787e208ccf51
          factId: fact_prototype_missing
          isTrue: 1
          evaluationRules: []
      - id: 777b0cae14e14920bd2c9255b7e7c458
        text: Actually, I did see something suspicious. Morgan was near my desk earlier,
          which was unusual.
        initiallyVisible: 0
        nextStatementId: 97cbb78e98ab40a2975d1c94367d6624
        claims:
        - id: ee7ff2ddf64e482cb00a78db19920e7b
          factId: fact_morgan_near_desk
          isTrue: 1
          evaluationRules:
          - evaluationType: 0
            requiredEvidence: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 48f5c87311d4240f4a0d669c42fcd02e, type: 2}
            successEffects:
            - effect: 8
              targetType: 0
              targetId: 
              courtStat: 7
              operation: 0
              characterStat: 0
              value: 2
            failureEffects:
            - effect: 8
              targetType: 0
              targetId: 
              courtStat: 0
              operation: 1
              characterStat: 0
              value: 2
    - id: 09c00afe4ddc413a9f0b012c96ec6d95
      title: The Backup Location
      description: Dr. Chen reveals where backups and duplicates might be stored.
      statements:
      - id: 5fb526c5dadc45a4bcbb3f34ea7ae16d
        text: There should be a backup prototype in Storage Room B. We always keep
          duplicates for testing.
        initiallyVisible: 1
        nextStatementId: 77132c3c61b74aaebdc89104af2bc524
        claims:
        - id: ba8a3dc8c5aa4feda563a2ac2fb82af5
          factId: fact_backup_exist
          isTrue: 1
          evaluationRules: []
      - id: d153d61179de474a84f757672df2bb3d
        text: I haven't checked if it's still there. With everything that happened,
          it slipped my mind.
        initiallyVisible: 1
        nextStatementId: eb598063d999428e98ae72ef8619062d
        claims: []
    initiallyVisible: 1
  - id: 7b25f7d950254b43b531d0f73d009dd4
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 87e3b180882784eaa972a917988a82c8, type: 2}
    role: 2
    description: Junior lab technician. Recently hired, still learning protocols.
    testimonies:
    - id: f3e4663c25664cc8912c59fefd35e9d4
      title: Morning Schedule
      description: Alex describes their activities during the morning.
      statements:
      - id: 166ccc09982c4753bee80e96bf13b0a5
        text: I arrived at 7:30 AM and went straight to check the equipment calibration
          logs.
        initiallyVisible: 1
        nextStatementId: 
        claims:
        - id: 7cd06f983afd419fb0af85970bbeb061
          factId: fact_alex_checked_equipment
          isTrue: 1
          evaluationRules: []
      - id: 2b097edd1b194559b34dfe943e8d5fe9
        text: Dr. Chen asked me to retrieve some archived data files around 8 AM.
          I was in the archive room for about 20 minutes."
        initiallyVisible: 1
        nextStatementId: 
        claims:
        - id: 7a84ddbd8bbd4bbabaa816b0cd1f42c9
          factId: fact_alex_in_archive
          isTrue: 1
          evaluationRules:
          - evaluationType: 0
            requiredEvidence: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 2c0d74d7ca190413a9e98fc4758fd5a7, type: 2}
            successEffects:
            - effect: 8
              targetType: 0
              targetId: 
              courtStat: 0
              operation: 0
              characterStat: 0
              value: 2
            failureEffects:
            - effect: 8
              targetType: 0
              targetId: 
              courtStat: 1
              operation: 0
              characterStat: 0
              value: 2
      - id: 99626e8a81e340ae925f2dae16eb8bbe
        text: I didn't see the prototype go missing. I was focused on my assigned
          tasks."
        initiallyVisible: 1
        nextStatementId: 616412e0e7e34a2dbf77d4977cd4655a
        claims:
        - id: 6b31ddb32e434ca881423eb55318ba77
          factId: fact_alex_didnt_see_theft
          isTrue: 1
          evaluationRules: []
    - id: a6008c5eb3354cbb801883584a682cde
      title: The Tool Request
      description: Alex mentions a tool that went missing after the prototype disappeared.
      statements:
      - id: 616412e0e7e34a2dbf77d4977cd4655a
        text: Wait, now that you mention it... Morgan asked me for a precision toolkit
          around 8:15 AM. That's unusual because Morgan usually doesn't work with
          lab equipment.
        initiallyVisible: 0
        nextStatementId: c03ede89f2b64ed99dfa2d82562d9fa3
        claims:
        - id: 456ad0fa777a4c468eceff4c779078da
          factId: fact_morgan_requested_tools
          isTrue: 1
          evaluationRules:
          - evaluationType: 0
            requiredEvidence: {fileID: 11400000, guid: e40e99ad9f1024c4c85c7ab1dda8cbd1, type: 2}
            successEffects:
            - effect: 9
              targetType: 5
              targetId: char_morgan
              courtStat: 0
              operation: 1
              characterStat: 0
              value: 10
            - effect: 9
              targetType: 5
              targetId: char_morgan
              courtStat: 0
              operation: 0
              characterStat: 2
              value: 10
            failureEffects:
            - effect: 9
              targetType: 5
              targetId: char_alex
              courtStat: 0
              operation: 1
              characterStat: 1
              value: 2
    initiallyVisible: 1
  - id: 3cd615131e494b898230f74ed1698b8f
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: e3f3b40b8bdd94036a28e011c2fbd718, type: 2}
    role: 0
    description: 
    testimonies:
    - id: 71b80c5ad57545cc8485b6cd91bc2ae2
      title: Security Rounds
      description: Morgan describes the morning security patrol.
      statements:
      - id: f408a635f60d48bbbf50a2cdbe95ef89
        text: I made my usual security rounds at 7 AM, 8 AM, and 9 AM. Everything
          was normal.
        initiallyVisible: 1
        nextStatementId: 
        claims:
        - id: 09e69436201b47a282a22b5bb7096bbf
          factId: fact_morgan_patrol
          isTrue: 1
          evaluationRules: []
      - id: 40924b0c080547be87572e2fbbde16a0
        text: I didn't go near Dr. Chen's desk at any point. I stick to the main
          corridors during my rounds.
        initiallyVisible: 1
        nextStatementId: c03ede89f2b64ed99dfa2d82562d9fa3
        claims:
        - id: bbfe63c64b3242d4bb9a5a5fa1871214
          factId: fact_morgan_not_at_desk
          isTrue: 1
          evaluationRules:
          - evaluationType: 2
            requiredEvidence: {fileID: 0}
            successEffects:
            - effect: 8
              targetType: 0
              targetId: 
              courtStat: 0
              operation: 0
              characterStat: 0
              value: 3
            - effect: 1
              targetType: 1
              targetId: 777b0cae14e14920bd2c9255b7e7c458
              courtStat: 0
              operation: 0
              characterStat: 0
              value: 0
            failureEffects:
            - effect: 8
              targetType: 0
              targetId: 
              courtStat: 1
              operation: 0
              characterStat: 1
              value: 3
      - id: eb598063d999428e98ae72ef8619062d
        text: I never touched the prototype. I don't even know how to operate it.
        initiallyVisible: 1
        nextStatementId: 777b0cae14e14920bd2c9255b7e7c458
        claims:
        - id: 539dd5d6bc0f4e41b2f16e0c2552f0b1
          factId: fact_morgan_no_knowledge
          isTrue: 1
          evaluationRules: []
    - id: d81b6c74db9845e38fd369fafe31971d
      title: Morgan Discovery
      description: Morgan reveals what happened after the theft was reported.
      statements:
      - id: 97cbb78e98ab40a2975d1c94367d6624
        text: When Dr. Chen reported the theft, I checked the access logs and found
          no unauthorized entries to the lab that morning.
        initiallyVisible: 1
        nextStatementId: 
        claims:
        - id: c08cef0f07924a70b9267d2575db1672
          factId: fact_no_unauthorized_access
          isTrue: 1
          evaluationRules: []
      - id: c03ede89f2b64ed99dfa2d82562d9fa3
        text: This means the person who took it had legitimate access to the building.
          It wasn't an outsider."
        initiallyVisible: 1
        nextStatementId: 
        claims:
        - id: 98e6fb43e3664b45b3544de471bdd599
          factId: fact_inside_job
          isTrue: 1
          evaluationRules:
          - evaluationType: 0
            requiredEvidence: {fileID: 0}
            successEffects:
            - effect: 0
              targetType: 0
              targetId: 
              courtStat: 0
              operation: 0
              characterStat: 0
              value: 0
            failureEffects: []
    initiallyVisible: 1
